<p>With summer coming to a close, the flavors and traditions of the fall season are just around the corner. Looking for a way to celebrate? Why not transform your favorite seasonal event into a Team Fox fundraiser? Check out some of our event ideas below for inspiration:</p>
<h2>More Fundraising Ideas</h2>
<ul class="listColumn1">
<li>Fall Harvest Potluck Supper</li>
<li>School Supplies Sale</li>
<li>Apple Cider and Doughnut Stand</li>
<li>Bowl-a-thon</li>
<li>School Talent Show</li>
<li>Children’s Art Auction</li>
<li>Walk to School Pledge-a-thon</li>
<li>Classroom Gift Basket Raffle</li>
<li>Pumpkin Carving Contest</li>
<li>Trivia Night</li>
</ul>
<ul class="listColumn2">
<li>5K Ride/Bike Event</li>
<li>Candy Apple Sale</li>
<li>Poetry Slam</li>
